summary: Half Dark Elf , half Redgaurd, exotic!
descriptionHtml:
I know a few people wanted this so here ya go.

Lore behind character is she's half Redgaurd, half Dark Elf, her full racial profile is Redguard though.

She should work as the other races, I know Nord looked fine.

Instalation; .zip contains the chargen profile for racemenu, install directly then load profile through racemenu in game.

Required mods;

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Race Menue[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]TheEyesofBeauty[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG EyeBrows[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdo's[/url]

She's not 100% perfect, low poly head, I tried to smooth the area around the corners of the mouth, to sort of have dimples, if you look reallly close you can see a flaw.

Feel free to let me know if you improve anything. Ill glady upload a new preset with your credit.

1080p Screen shots are taken with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG FemaleRenwal skin[/url], and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70196/?]my own ENB[/url] with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70451/?]Snapdrgaon DoF[/url]
author: TheGloriousArgonaut
